  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      study hypothesis to examine the acute effects on glycaemia and islet hormone secretion of
      increased levels of endogenous GLP-1 and GIP on islet cell function in men with type 2
      diabetes. To this purpose, a standardized mixed meal test will be ingested with or without
      concomitant administration of sitagliptin (100mg).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      In men subjects with type 2 diabetes treated with diet and exercise with or without metformin
      treatment as an antidiabetic agent, a standardized mixed meal test will be served with or
      without administration of sitagliptin (100mg).
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
